On Oct 6, 2005, at 7:08 AM, David Hopkins wrote:

> so.. the question is, should i sand blast or have them acid dipped?
> and can i still find someone that will acid dip them?

If they are very rusted, after you de-rest them you'll probably be  
let with pitting, that if painted will leave an imperfect finish.

FYI, the stock of new VW of Mexico steel wheels seems to be running  
out. I don't think they were the right color anyway.

